  "title": "Azure SQL Database Ledger",
  "contentHtml": "In this special episode Michael and Sarah talk with guest Pieter Vanhove&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/pieter-vanhove-1756169/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/Pieter_Vanhove'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about Azure SQL DB Ledger functionality that was released today at the <a href='https://mybuild.microsoft.com/en-US/home'>Microsoft BUILD Conference.</a> \n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/497207?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/497207/\">Azure SQL Database Ledger</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/497207/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/ledger-now-generally-available-in-azure-sql-database/ba-p/3379658\">Azure SQL Database Ledger now available</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/resources/-sql-ledger-cryptographically-verifiable-data-in-azure-sql-database-/\">Maintain Cryptographically Verifiable Data in Azure SQL Database</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/ledger-database-ledger?view=azuresql\">What is the database ledger?</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://customers.microsoft.com/en-us/story/1497685499820529889-lenovo-manufacturing-azure-SQL-database-ledger\">Lenovo reinforces customer trust with ledger in Azure SQL Database</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://customers.microsoft.com/en-us/story/1379614319255768839-rtgs-partner-professional-services-azure-sql\">RTGS.global automates financial transfers, unlocks trillions in capital with Azure</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/sql-server-samples/tree/master/samples/features/security/ledger\">Demos of Ledger</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/architecture/guide/technology-choices/multiparty-computing-service#comparing-options\">Comparing options: Confidential Ledger and Azure SQL Database ledger</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/storage/blobs/immutable-storage-overview\">Store business-critical blob data with immutable storage</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
